  "title": "Harmonic Maiden",
  "description": "Today we've got a very special guest!\n\nRight as the Super Idol Mirai finishes her introduction, the Ultra-Super Idol Anya makes her grand appearance. The cheers are deafening. Some fans even faint on the spot just from seeing Anya standing there.\n\n\"All right, let's do our usual song!\"\n\nIn perfect unison, the crowd raises their glow sticks and braces themselves in silence. Anya grips the microphone. One deep breath.\n\n\"Boom-boom, tss-tss, chicka-chicka-tss!\"\n\nAnya—the idol who rose to the very top of the industry through sheer vocal percussion!\nAnd today's performance? She's in top form!",
